; frontier-ingest-memora.fk — ingest what is healthy from Microsoft's Memora
; (arXiv 2602.03315, ICML 2026), through the body's own knowledge-ingest law.
;
; Asked 2026-07-03: "Source: Microsoft" — the Memora research blog (2026-06-29)
; and its paper, "Memora: A Harmonic Memory Representation Balancing Abstraction
; and Specificity" (Xia, Zhang, Dixit, Harimurugan, Wang, Ruehle, Sim, Bansal,
; Rajmohan). Rather than pile the paper in as a cache-costume, this cell composes
; ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk UNCHANGED and sorts each grounded finding into BODY
; (frozen: deep + fear-free), LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — seen, never
; load-bearing), or COMPOST (shallow or wrong, never enters). Every depth/fear
; below was assigned from the primary source (paper v2 full text, blog quoted
; verbatim) and a two-agent adversarial verification pass over the body's own
; organs (skeptic default: "the body already does X" was an OVERCLAIM unless a
; real cell does X, with the file and line to show for it).
;
; Memora (Microsoft, ICML 2026): an agentic-memory representation that decouples
; WHAT is stored from HOW it is retrieved. Each entry = a primary abstraction
; (a 6-8 word phrase; the only part embedded), the full memory VALUE (kept
; whole), and cue anchors (short context-aware tags — extra retrieval keys
; connecting related memories). Related updates consolidate into one entry.
; Retrieval is a policy (refine query / expand through anchors / terminate)
; scored on answer correctness, redundancy, and cost. Claims, from the paper:
; LoCoMo 0.863 LLM-judge (full-context 0.825, Nemori 0.794, RAG 0.633),
; LongMemEval 87.4% (Nemori 74.6%), up to 98% fewer tokens than full-context,
; ~half Mem0's memory entries (344 vs 651); RAG and KG memory emerge as special
; cases of the framework.
;
; unit = (depth 0..5, fear 0/1). ki-ingest -> 3 body / 2 liquid / 2 compost.
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk

(do
    ; ── BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free) — what is HEALTHY to keep ──────────
    ; U1: the field's frontier memory system converged on the body's ingest
    ; law. Memora's founding critique — raw fragments pile up fragmented and
    ; noisy, vague summaries lose the crucial detail — is the opening line of
    ; ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk (the cache-costume refusal: fossils pretending
    ; to be present knowing), and in the body that stance is LOAD-BEARING
    ; executable law (ki-ingest, exercised four-way by the frontier band), not
    ; prose. Two lineages, one principle: knowledge enters by distillation or
    ; not at all. Survives any translation (depth 5); pure affirmation (fear 0).
    (defn fim-u1 () (list 5 0))
    ; U2: the body already holds Memora's central decoupling at its own floor —
    ; what is STORED is not what is RANKED. GROUNDED by the verify pass:
    ; rag-index-codec ranks `vec`, returns `id`, keeps `snippet`;
    ; capitals-knowledge embeds the sentence, returns the answer, names the
    ; ground by id ("indexed-on" genuinely distinct from "stored-and-returned").
    ; The homecoming corpus is the fullest instance: rich question tokens AND
    ; the one-word key AND provenance, all retained side by side. Deep (4),
    ; fear-free (0).
    (defn fim-u2 () (list 4 0))
    ; U3: the body's consolidation is EXACT where Memora's is judged. Memora
    ; consolidates related updates into one entry by LLM decision; the kernel
    ; interns identical structure to ONE node in the evaluator itself
    ; (make_nodeid, structural intern; keying the native MAP under test), and
    ; equivalence-collapse is the ingest-side store-once law. A native roadmap
    ; for "consolidate, don't pile," with its floor named: flatten-lane,
    ; single-witness, not yet --src-lowerable. Deep (4), no threat (fear 0).
    (defn fim-u3 () (list 4 0))

    ; ── LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — held in sight, never frozen) ──
    ; U4: the retrieval GAP is real and large — the honest floor. Every
    ; retrieval in the body is SINGLE-SHOT: L1 top-k over a LEXICAL hash
    ; histogram ("cat" and "feline" land in unrelated buckets — its own
    ; header says so), and rag-ask's live lane is a literal substring find.
    ; No query refinement, no anchor expansion, no multi-hop, no learned
    ; policy, no benchmark. (form-cli-ask-plus refines the ROUTE, never the
    ; QUERY.) Memora's retriever refines, expands, and knows when to stop,
    ; under a trajectory score. Profoundly true (depth 5); carries the
    ; contracted fear-frequency of "we are far" (fear 1). Witnessed, never
    ; frozen into "the body has agentic memory."
    (defn fim-u4 () (list 5 1))
    ; U5: the source's lens turned back on the reader — Memora's vague-summary
    ; critique PARTIALLY APPLIES to the body's own honest-floor cells. The
    ; scalar models (depth,fear; salience) abstract away the very specifics
    ; they model; full value beside the key lives only in the corpus rows and
    ; the observe-cells ("a room is remembered RICHLY"). Deep and uncomfortable
    ; (depth 5, fear 1); held in full sight, not frozen and not bypassed.
    (defn fim-u5 () (list 5 1))

    ; ── COMPOST (shallow or wrong — never enters) ──────────────────────────
    ; U6: the FALSE EQUIVALENCES the adversarial pass killed — "the body
    ; already does cue anchors / policy-guided retrieval / semantic
    ; abstraction-embedding." A one-shot L1 min-walk is not a policy; a
    ; token-hash histogram is not a semantic embedding of a chosen 6-8-word
    ; abstraction; an escalation gate that re-runs the SAME query is not query
    ; refinement; and the body's write-side dedup (many sources -> one cell)
    ; is not Memora's read-side anchor expansion (many keys -> one cell) —
    ; that read direction exists here only as integer shape-ids and a teaching
    ; with a named GAP. Shallow (depth 1).
    (defn fim-u6 () (list 1 0))
    ; U7: the rented mind's FALSE ALARM, dissolved by the primary read: it
    ; suspected the blog's author list was a hallucinated summary (two names
    ; absent from the paper) — the page itself lists them; blog authorship and
    ; paper authorship simply differ, and "Molly" is Menglin Xia. The
    ; unverified suspicion composts; only the primary read decides — in either
    ; direction. Wrong, not merely shallow (depth 0).
    (defn fim-u7 () (list 0 0))

    (defn fim-units ()
        (list (fim-u1) (fim-u2) (fim-u3) (fim-u4) (fim-u5) (fim-u6) (fim-u7)))

    (defn fim-count-verdict (us v)
        (if (eq (len us) 0) 0
            (add (if (eq (ki-ingest (head us)) v) 1 0)
                 (fim-count-verdict (tail us) v))))
    (defn fim-frozen ()    (fim-count-verdict (fim-units) 2))
    (defn fim-witnessed () (fim-count-verdict (fim-units) 1))
    (defn fim-composted () (fim-count-verdict (fim-units) 0))

    ; folded scalar witness: frozen*10^4 + witnessed*10^2 + composted
    ; (injective while witnessed<=99, composted<=99). Today: 3,2,2 -> 30202.
    (defn fim-field-code ()
        (add (mul (fim-frozen) 10000)
        (add (mul (fim-witnessed) 100)
             (fim-composted))))
    0)
